article_title: New report warns against Texas Medicaid expansion
article_text:
New report warns against Texas Medicaid expansion

Photo: Uncredited, HOPD This is the home page for HealthCare,gov where Texans can go to...

A report released Wednesday urges state lawmakers to continue rejecting Medicaid expansion to cover more uninsured Texans and push for some kind of private insurance program that would be more affordable.
